    verification vamRetroGate : Test { :>> id = "63940516-2c7d-4e8f-c223-51627384c00e"; :>> title = "Sprint 223 retro gate (autonomous, D0049)"; :>> createdAt = "2026-07-15"; :>> createdBy = "claudeOpus"; :>> method = VerificationMethod::analyze; :>> procedureText = "Autonomous retro (D0049). WELL: delivered a genuinely generative MVP (not a hardcoded viewer) and verified it in a real browser, not just by asserting endpoints. AVOIDABLE-ISSUE (the user's correction, now a banked lesson + memory): I built + committed the app but had NOT recorded it via governance — recording is PART of the task, not a later step. Fixed by authoring D0118 + this sprint in the SAME effort going forward. Also: [hidden] is overridden by an explicit CSS display — set display:none in the [hidden] rule. LESSON: for every deliverable, author its Decision + delivery sprint + satisfy edges as it is produced; unrecorded work is not done. Estimate 5 pts. NEXT: notation research → axis-encoding viewpoints."; }
    part vamRetroGateR1 : TestResult { :>> id = "63940516-2c7d-4e8f-c223-51627384c00f"; :>> outcome = VerdictKind::pass; :>> judgedAgainst = "33beb77"; :>> judgedAt = "2026-07-15"; :>> judgedBy = "claudeOpus"; }
